ho is currently licensed under Division 2 (commencing with Section 500) of the Business and Professions Code.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(22) An emergency medical technician I or II, paramedic, or other person certified pursuant to Division 2.5 (commencing with Section 1797) of the Health and Safety Code.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(23) A psychological assistant registered pursuant to Section 2913 of the Business and Professions Code.</div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;margin-left: 1em;">(24) A marriage and family therapist trainee, as defined in subdivision
